&lt;p>Implement robust retry mechanisms with exponential backoff:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>API Design Patterns for Modern Applications</title><link>https://scottobert.com/posts/api-design-patterns-modern-applications/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Sep 2021 11:00:00 -0700</pubDate><guid>https://scottobert.com/posts/api-design-patterns-modern-applications/</guid><description>&lt;p>Modern API design has evolved far beyond simple CRUD operations. Today&amp;rsquo;s applications require APIs that are resilient, scalable, and developer-friendly while supporting diverse client needs and complex business workflows. This guide explores proven patterns that address these challenges.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="foundational-design-principles">Foundational Design Principles&lt;/h2>
